Moven Mahachi said here Tuesday that the Zimbabwean forces in the
Democratic Republic of Congo (DRC) have captured 40 Rwandan
soldiers and have brought them to Zimbabwe.
</P>
<P>
The minister said that his government was negotiating with
Rwanda for the release of 16 Zimbabwean soldiers who were captured
by the Uganda and Rwanda-backed rebels in the DRC in exchange of
the Rwandan soldiers in Zimbabwe.
</P>
