71 million U.S. dollars will be put on offer to foreign investors
in the forum. Of these, 19 are in agricultural and industrial
sectors,
</P>
<P>
"In particular, we're encouraging the agro-industrial sector
because we see real potential for exports," said Hafez, adding
the response in that area has been very promising.
</P>
<P>
