12, 1964 in a bloody revolution in Zanzibar. Three months later,
Zanzibar united with Tanganyika forming a united Tanzania.
</P>
<P>
A popular tourist destination consisting of two major islands,
Zanzibar and Pemba, along with several other smaller islands in
the Indian Ocean, Zanzibar i{
5nhabited by nearly one million
residents, more than 90 percent of which are Moslems.
