eight, beating Israel's Anna Smashnova 6-2, 4-6, 6-1.
</P>
<P>
With Nathalie Dechy having progressed Tuesday, France has
three players in the quarter-finals.
</P>
<P>
Australia's Nicole Pratt and American Amy Frazier were to
decide the final quarter-finalist later Wednesday. 
