contest will encourage local government executives, particularly
the governors and mayors, to successfully implement their food
security programs.
</P>
<P>
Estrada also signed an executive order creating food security
councils at national and provincial levels, Dar said.
</P>
<P>
Meanwhile, the country's 78 governors signed a Food Security
Covenant, pledging to help the Estrada administration attain
self-sufficiency in food production. 
</P>
