<HEADLINE> Mother Baboon Kills Her Baby in Zoo </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, January 13 (Xinhua) -- An Arabian baboon in the
Chongqing Zoo recently ate her newborn cub as visitors to the zoo
looked on, according to the latest issue of the Yangcheng Evening
News.
</P>
<P>
Zoo workers said they were surprising at this extreme behavior
of the mother baboon who had been taking good care of her
one-month-old baby, the Guangzhou-based paper said.
</P>
<P>
According to local sources, this was the second such incident
among the baboons in the zoo. Previously, a male baboon with a
high position in the ape hierarchy violently tore a younger
baboon to pieces.
</P>
<P>
Experts say that many males in the animal kingdom take to
killing younger members of their species who threaten their
social position.
</P>
<P>
However, they could not explain the eccentric behavior of this
mother killer, and scientists plan to investigate further, the
newspaper said.
</P>
</TEXT>
