continued. "In the past several years the good-neighborly
relationships of mutual benefit between the two countries have
seen overall and positive development, to which you yourself have
made major contributions," said Jiang.
</P>
<P>
The Chinese president voiced his willingness to work together
with Nazarbayev to further promote the advancement of the
bilateral links so as to benefit the people of the two countries.
