<HEADLINE> Portugal Sees Less Jobless People </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
According to figures published by the nation's employment and
occupational training authorities, an average of some 400,000 job
seekers registered with job centers per month in 1998, down 9.5
percent from a year earlier.
</P>
<P>
